sumenten als auch gegenüber den Händlern, und zwar online wie offline.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 15. Jun 2019) 4aCustomer orientation. 4aCustomer. 4aKundenorientierung. 4aMarketing. 4aRetail Development. 4aRetail development. 4aSales. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Marketing / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG OWV ebook Paket Lehrbücher Wirtschaftswiss. 2018z9783110603262oZDB-23-OLW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics 2018z9783110603101oZDB-23-DBV0 cEPUBz97831105360890 cprintz978311053576140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110535730423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110535730.jpg  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA14ALL  aPDA15STM  aPDA16SSH  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2HUM  aPDA3STM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DBVb2018  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-OLWb2018